description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are to: (i) improve the basic conditions of welfare and social well-being of extremely poor beneficiary families with children in Selected Poor Localities; (ii) strengthen the capacity of MIFAN to implement the family andcommunity-based social welfare Model; and (iii) promote pre-school and primary school attendance through the provision of schoollunches.
